ae2bfe849330d83a1a2824b0f","tid":1577930,"uid":156914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T13:26:27.000Z","msg":"我願榮光歸香港"},{"pid":"fcf7221f6cc15b393bd35a386ae2fd374fdfa9eb","tid":1577930,"uid":30115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T13:30:55.000Z","msg":"我願榮光歸香港 為香港呢個我地成長既地方 即使要上戰場 我地無所畏懼"},{"pid":"a7876d790e231f02cb15b6b6c0c72d9c68098372","tid":1577930,"uid":121100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T13:35:58.000Z","msg":"人生第一次知原來唱歌係會喊"},{"pid":"9edcdb99e9cb1d74cd1806c3f863b6181efe035e","tid":1577930,"uid":53612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T13:38:22.000Z","msg":"何以這土地淚再流"},{"pid":"2c4d667272642fa79e255c99c2ebec0981b64672","tid":1577930,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T13:38:49.000Z","msg":"何以 這土地 淚再流<br />\n何以 令眾人 亦憤恨<br />\n昂首 拒默沉 吶喊聲 響透<br />\n盼自由 歸於 這裡<br />\n<br />\n何以 這恐懼 抹不走<br />\n何以 為信念 從沒退後<br />\n何解 血在流 但邁進聲 響透<br />\n建自由 光輝 香港<br />\n<br />\n在晚星 墜落 徬徨午夜<br />\n迷霧裡 最遠處吹來 號角聲<br />\n捍自由 來齊集這裡 來全力抗對<br />\n勇氣 智慧 也永不滅<br />\n<br />\n黎明來到 要光復 這香港<br />\n同行兒女 為正義 時代革命<br />\n祈求 民主與自由 萬世都不朽<br />\n我願榮光歸香港<br />\n<br />\n光復香港！時代革命！<br />\n光復香港！時代革命！<br />\n光復香港！時代革命！<br />\n<br />\n多謝！<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7af6ed1224c5539c51e349df28dca5a6510a2230","tid":1577930,"uid":33984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T13:39:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0b9f3cc3829c95a7adb536204299ac677e1f8a2","tid":1577930,"uid":10200,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T13:41:43.000Z","msg":"因為係第一首以香港人身分為主體 而又有咁強群眾意識同政治味道嘅歌"},{"pid":"518442cc13a5ec5a0dcbca5df899418de1b7793e","tid":1577930,"uid":47110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T13:44:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"958eeb0133f7d57c901ee8bd8d9ca873b9313d2d","tid":1577930,"uid":193215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T13:52:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf558f198b72ae7c6deb7242cc78ebc068acf6eb","tid":1577930,"uid":81996,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T13:57:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f49e69cf59464848807e72b0eadcddf7b8c6b64a","tid":1577930,"uid":288154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T11:32:18.000Z","msg":"《願榮光歸香港》香港電台 十大中文金曲 2019<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1582707\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1582707</a>"},{"pid":"188575c2bc00e425cf992b3a420c09b3e51c10e3","tid":1577930,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T12:20:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca5285ecfe9038e822dc2bdf417f76b19b047256","tid":1577930,"uid":211034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T12:38:10.000Z","msg":"一齊去Twitter將 #929globalantichinazimarch <br />\n推上熱門 <br />\n推到929全世界所有人都一齊standwithHK<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mjKZ7PA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmjKZ7PA.jpg&h=9c9f7bc8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5sn1BHW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5sn1BHW.jpg&h=f59429dc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/stjbYWh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FstjbYWh.jpg&h=231ca5f7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QW0OgHY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQW0OgHY.jpg&h=d6c222cc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/opCg92Z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FopCg92Z.jpg&h=5bd6bb90&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1dbb8016b5a944175ed453f14fa334819fc6d385","tid":1577930,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T13:15:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}